Manage your team's subscription and view usage information.

## Accessing Team Billing

1. Ensure you're in your team account
1. Click **Billing** in the sidebar
1. The URL is `https://sellfaster.eu/home/[team]/billing`

> **Note:** Billing access requires the `billing.manage` permission, which is restricted to team owners.

